ZH: 我家厨房的炉灶很好用。
EN: The stove in my kitchen is very user-friendly.

ZH: 她正在炉灶上煮汤。
EN: She is boiling soup on the stove.

ZH: 这个炉灶是用来烹饪食物的。
EN: This stove is used for cooking food.

ZH: 请确保关闭炉灶后再离开厨房。
EN: Please make sure to turn off the stove before leaving the kitchen.

ZH: 这个炉灶是新的，很干净。
EN: This stove is new and very clean.

ZH: 炉灶上的火焰很大。
EN: The flame on the stove is very strong.

ZH: 请小心炉灶，不要烫到自己。
EN: Please be careful with the stove, so you don't burn yourself.

ZH: 厨师站在炉灶前面烹饪美食。
EN: The chef is cooking delicious food in front of the stove.

ZH: 她在炉灶上煎了一块牛排。
EN: She fried a steak on the stove.

ZH: 这个炉灶是用煤气的。
EN: This stove is gas-powered.

ZH: 他把平底锅放在炉灶上。
EN: He placed the saucepan on the stove.

ZH: 这个炉灶易于清洁。
EN: This stove is easy to clean.

ZH: 灶具前放了一张椅子，可以坐着看火防止烧焦的情况。
EN: A chair is placed in front of the stove to sit and watch to prevent burning.

ZH: 她打开了炉灶，开始做晚饭。
EN: She turned on the stove and started cooking dinner.

ZH: 我的炉灶需要修理，无法正常使用。
EN: My stove needs repair and cannot be used normally.

ZH: 厨房炉灶的火苗被吹灭了。
EN: The flame on the kitchen stove was blown out.

ZH: 这个炉灶可以调节火力。
EN: This stove can adjust the firepower.

ZH: 她用擦拭布擦拭了炉灶上的油渍。
EN: She wiped off the oil stains on the stove with a cleaning cloth.

ZH: 他不小心把手放在炉灶上烫伤了。
EN: He accidentally burnt his hand on the stove.

ZH: 这个炉灶是电动的。
EN: This stove is electric-powered.
